NAME: employeeNumber
SELECT_STAT: SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_NUMBER value ,e.EMPLOYEE_NUMBER FROM EMPLOYEES e

NAME: CategoryID
SELECT_STAT:
select cat.CATEGORY_ID,cat.CATEGORY_NAME

from CATEGORIES cat

where cat.is_enabled = 'Y'

NAME: ISAgent
SELECT_STAT:
select 'Y' isagent , 'نعم' agent 

from dual 

union 

select 'N'isagent , 'لا' agent 

from dual

NAME: EmployeeTypeID
SELECT_STAT:
select ET.EMPLOYEES_TYPE_ID , ET.EMPLOYEES_TYPE_NAME

from employees_types et

where ET.IS_ENABLED='Y'

NAME: categoryId
SELECT_STAT:
select cat.CATEGORY_ID,cat.CATEGORY_NAME

from CATEGORIES cat

where cat.is_enabled = 'Y'

NAME: IS_Agent
SELECT_STAT:
select 'Y' isagent , 'نعم' agent 

from dual 

union 

select 'N'isagent , 'لا' agent 

from dual
